metadata.name: Immortal Flame EURO21NFT All Flag Edition
metadata.description:
Mystical Series: Immortal Flame EURO21NFT All Flag Edition
This Unique ERC721 can be redeemed when collectors have every 24 countries of EURO21NFT.
EURO21NFT was created to record this memorable Euro2020/2021 event. High collective value, limited supply to all the football & NFT fans in the world. All unsold EURO21NFT will be burned after the final match of Euro2020. A collector can redeem Unique ERC-721 and Mystical EURO21NFT on our website if they collect all 24 countries EURO21NFT.
Check us out on www.euro21nft.com and find us in Discord and also Twitter.
